-- analyst-debate.cell: Experiment 3 вЂ” Multi-analyst synthesis
-- Two analysts study the same citizen data from different theoretical frameworks.
-- A third synthesizer reconciles their findings.
-- Tests: multi-layer soft cell dispatch, parallel analysts, synthesis step

вЉў city
  yield description в‰Ў "Millhaven, a small coastal town. Harbor, main street, residential hill, lighthouse."
  yield day в‰Ў "Tuesday, March 4"

вЉў citizen-sam
  given cityв†’description
  given cityв†’day
  yield name в‰Ў "Sam Okafor"
  yield age в‰Ў 45
  yield occupation в‰Ў "owner of the hardware store on Main Street"
  yield morning
  yield afternoon
  yield evening
  yield thoughts
  в€ґ You are В«nameВ», age В«ageВ», В«occupationВ» in Millhaven.
    Town: В«descriptionВ». Today is В«dayВ».
    Live your day. Morning, afternoon, evening. Share your private thoughts.
    Be specific about places and people. Concise but vivid.
  вЉЁ morning is a string
  вЉЁ thoughts is a string

